# tutorial.dtl
audio music "res://assets/audio/ambient/wind_outside.wav" [fade="2.0" volume="-5.0" bus="Music"]
[background arg="res://assets/narrative/checkpoint_interior.png" fade="0.0"]
join narrator [z_index="1"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Welcome to [color=MEDIUM_VIOLET_RED]Spud Customs Training![/color]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Your duty is to process incoming potatoes at our border checkpoint.
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: This training will teach you the [color=DARK_ORANGE]essential skills[/color] needed to protect Spud's borders.
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: As a Customs Officer, you'll need to check documents carefully.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/mega_phone_example.png" fade="1.5"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: You'll signal each potato to approach your office by tapping the megaphone.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/suspect_panel_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Take their documents and move them to your inspection table.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/examine_document_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Look for [color=YELLOW]expired dates, incorrect information, or signs of forgery[/color].
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Your desk has stamps for marking documents and an uplink to control [color=CRIMSON]missile launchers to defend the wall[/color].

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/stamp_bar_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: To use a stamp, expand the stamp tray and drag a document underneath, then click the stamp.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/align_stamp_example.png" fade="0.8"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Be sure to place your documents in the designated areas underneath your stamps.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/apply_stamp_example.png" fade="0.8"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Use your stamps to mark documents as [color=CHARTREUSE]approved[/color] or [color=CRIMSON]rejected[/color].

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/reject_stamp_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Approve those with valid papers and reject those without.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/border_runner_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Sometimes, potatoes will try to [color=CRIMSON]rush past your checkpoint[/color].

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/explode_runner_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Click on these "runners" to launch a missile and stop them.

[background arg="res://assets/tutorial/strikes_quota_example.png" fade="1.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Remember, each runner that gets through will count as a [color=CRIMSON]strike against you[/color].
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Too many strikes, and your shift will end... [color=CRIMSON]permanently.[/color]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Each shift has a [color=DARK_ORANGE]quota of potatoes[/color] you need to process to finish your day.

[background arg="res://assets/narrative/checkpoint_interior.png" fade="2.0"]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: That covers the basics of your duties as a Customs Officer.
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Remember\: check documents carefully, stop runners, and meet your quota.
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_a_keyboard_3.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: The safety and security of Spud depends on your [color=DARK_ORANGE]vigilance![/color]
audio "res://assets/audio/talking/typing_on_old_keyboard_2.wav" [volume="-5.0" bus="SFX"]
narrator: Good luck, officer.
leave narrator